202106 : 15
```

***Note:** the more efficient approach is to adjust the values in the `monthCaseCountSorted` map. And streams are not appropriate for such a task. Functions must not cause side effects and every execution of the function must have the same outcome (if you&#39;ll try to implement a stream-based solution by changing values in the `monthCaseCountSorted` directly both these conditions will be violated)*

